comments: O'Neale (UTA) places an arm on Redick (NOP) and affects his FOM off ball.
Gobert (UTA) slightly extends his arm into Moore (NOP) while disengaging from the pick.
Favors (NOP) has a resting arm on Gobert's (UTA) body and cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Redick (NOP) and Bogdanovic (UTA) make marginal contact with one another as they move through the screen.
Mitchell (UTA) makes marginal contact with Ball (NOP) while he fights over the pick.
Ball (NOP) delivers some contact to Bogdanovic (UTA) during the pick.
Redick (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gobert (UTA) and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Ball (NOP) makes slight contact with O'Neale's (UTA) arm after he gathered the rebound.
Favors (NOP) and Gobert (UTA) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Ingles (UTA) briefly grabs Favors' (NOP) arm while fighting around the screen.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Ingram's (NOP) arm during his shot attempt.
